name: Marshall Strawberry includes 2-day shipping
description:
Order now for spring! Plants will be shipped April, 2014. 
Gift certificates available for holiday gift giving. 

Price INCLUDES 2-day shipping.

James Beard described the Marshall as the "tastiest strawberry in America", just few short years ago was listed on Slow Foods Most Endangered Foods List.  Help Leah revive this national treasure by adopting a live rare Marshall Strawberry plant.  

Each numbered plant comes in a handmade container, suitable for gift giving, along with a certificate of authenticity and signature of the artist. 

See http://www.marshallstrawberry for the whole story on Marshall.
